metadata.name: Dreams of the New World
metadata.description:
“Soft mist attracts and soothes.
I want to drown in it and not wake up. 
Few flowers are reminiscent of Earth, but the crystals and holographic sky speak of something new.”

I explore the theme of sleep as an escape from reality. When you want to fall asleep and wake up in a new beautiful future.

But you either wake up where there are no guarantees, or you may not wake up at all.

Anna Bell x AI
2023
